            icon: 'tabler:checks',
          },
          {
            description:
              '<a class="underline" target="_blank" href="https://github.com/rustdesk/rustdesk/wiki/FAQ#what-are-managed-devices--licensed-users--concurrent-connections-in-pro">10 usuários licenciados</a>',
          },
          {
            description:
